"gs(109262)\">Rom. 3:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109296\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109296)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109296)\">Rom. 8:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109550\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109550)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109550)\">1 Cor. 13:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109740\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109740)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109740)\">Gal. 4:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110109\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110109)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110109)\">Titus 3:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112755\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112755)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112755)\">4 Ne. 1:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116967\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116967)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116967)\">Abr. 1:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">25. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108336\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108336)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108336)\">Mark 7:8-9,13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115050\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115050)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115050)\">D&amp;C 93:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}